## 1. Asset Attestation
### 1.1 Real-World Asset Onboarding
#### A. Stable-Pegged
- 【Compliant Fiat Stablecoins / CBDC】: Mapped 1:1 with issuance reserves, integrated into unified clearing, interoperable with all assets.
- Mandatory Proof-of-Reserve (PoR): issuer must provide on-chain verifiable 1:1 reserve proof, audited in real time; reserve ratio < 100% suspends swapping.
- Redemption Right: holders may redeem anchored assets 1:1 to real fiat at any time; redemption channel must be permanent and unclosable by any single party.
#### B. Volatile (no 1:1 promise)
- 【Bitcoin / Gold etc.】: booked at real-time fair value at onboarding, bound to unique `nft_dna`; redeemed at real-time market value on exit.
- Fixed-supply assets (e.g. BTC 21,000,000) are mirrored on-chain records only, not granted "value-stable" property.
### 1.2 Virtual World Assets
- Platform currencies/points/tokens auto-map to Nohn standard assets upon submitting total supply + circulation proof; ownership bound to `GlobalIdentity.soul_hash`.
- NFT/props generate unique `ASSET_ID` recording creator/attributes/history/permissions; duplication is invalid.
## 2. Universal Value Swap
- Unit of account: `NOHN_POINT`. Anchored assets swap 1:1 to real reserves; volatile assets convert at real-time market value.
- Cross-world/real swapping: 1:1 value anchoring for anchored assets, no forced fees, no loss, instant, fully traceable.
## 3. Supply Control
- New issuance requires value endorsement + use description, audited before circulation. Destruction is permanently logged.
## 4. Reserve Custody & Redemption
- Custody via on-chain PoR multi-sig/contract; no single-entity custody. Redemption 1:1 anytime; bankruptcy-isolated reserves.
## 5. Oracle & Valuation
- ≥3 independent oracles, median/weighted average, on-chain signed; anomaly triggers circuit breaker.
## 6. Asset Identifier Schema
- `soul_hash`: SHA-256, 64 hex. `ASSET_ID`: `ASSET-<chain>-<sha256(...)>`. `nft_dna`: on-chain fingerprint.
